Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:53.97,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur1}記憶之扉敞開的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:56.00,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur1}你想一同聆聽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.06,0:02:00.21,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)\blur1}我便傾訴於你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:09.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}啊 雖然這般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:12.90,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}重要的回憶也會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.97,0:02:16.65,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}被時間之沙掩蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.71,0:02:20.91,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}而變得曖昧不明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.94,0:02:27.56,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}說著「命運」這詞是如此廉價
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.65,0:02:31.93,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}而與我一同開懷大笑的你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:37.41,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}又是否是我生命中的羅密歐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:42.14,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}大家 一定會將自己的珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:45.95,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}逐漸忘卻在心的角落
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:49.02,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}與你的一分一秒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:52.94,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}即使只有一瞬 也請留在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:56.40,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}即使成為無法集齊的拼圖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.49,0:03:00.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}那無法尋覓的最後一片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.26,0:03:03.28,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}記憶之扉敞開的聲音
